 I'M MEANT TO BE WORKING ON OUR GAME BUT I FELT DISC 116 WAS
 A CRAP NUMBER TO STOP ON. I HOPE TO GET TO DISC 120 BEFORE I
 STOP FOR A REST.        I'VE ALREADY CODED AN INTRO FOR OUR
 FUTURE PRODUCTIONS, I DID IT ON AN ALL NIGHT CODING SESSION
 WHICH ENDED AT 5 AM. THE RESULT WAS AN INTRO DIRECTLY CONVERTED
 FROM A CYBERPAINT SEQUENCE, THE CODING WASN'T HARD BUT IT
 DID REQUIRE SOME PATIENTS AS I HAD TO GO BACK AND FORTH
 BETWEEN CYBERPAINT AND DEVPAC UNTIL IT WAS EXACTLY THE SAME. ALL
 I NEED NOW IS SOME MUSIC AND IT WILL BE FINISHED.
